<tt xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml" xmlns:itunes="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal" xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" xmlns:tts="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#styling" xmlns:amll="http://www.example.com/ns/amll" itunes:timing="Word"><head><metadata><ttm:agent type="person" xml:id="v1"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="Mine (Illenium Remix)"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="Mine (Remix)"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="ILLENIUM"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="Phoebe Ryan"/><amll:meta key="album" value="Mine (ILLENIUM Remix)"/><amll:meta key="album" value="Mine (Remix)"/><amll:meta key="ncmMusicId" value="30780496"/><amll:meta key="qqMusicId" value="001eZJB14ALyBx"/><amll:meta key="appleMusicId" value="1788214329"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithub" value="158539001"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithubLogin" value="PhantomPixel-0418"/><iTunesMetadata xmlns="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal"><songwriters><songwriter>Phoebe Ryan</songwriter><songwriter>Kyle Shearer</songwriter><songwriter>Nathaniel Campany</songwriter></songwriters></iTunesMetadata></metadata></head><body dur="3:34.181"><div begin="20.940" end="3:34.181"><p begin="20.940" end="22.515" itunes:key="L1" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="20.940" end="21.255">When</span> <span begin="21.255" end="21.495">it</span> <span begin="21.495" end="21.860">went</span> <span begin="21.860" end="22.515">down</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">当我堕落的时候</span></p><p begin="23.365" end="25.810" itunes:key="L2" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="23.365" end="23.552">It</span> <span begin="23.552" end="23.788">was</span> <span begin="23.788" end="24.270">so</span> <span begin="24.270" end="24.866">hard</span> <span begin="24.866" end="25.201">to</span> <span begin="25.201" end="25.810">breathe</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我被桎梏在这无形的悲伤里 喘不过气</span></p><p begin="25.810" end="28.790" itunes:key="L3" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="25.810" end="26.101">I</span> <span begin="26.101" end="26.430">gave</span> <span begin="26.430" end="26.729">up</span> <span begin="26.729" end="27.860">everything</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">曾经为此放弃一切</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="27.938" end="28.790"><span begin="27.938" end="28.790">(Everything)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">一切</span></span></p><p begin="28.526" end="32.200" itunes:key="L4" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="28.526" end="28.791">And</span> <span begin="28.791" end="28.891">I</span> <span begin="28.891" end="29.616">slow</span> <span begin="29.965" end="30.584">fall</span> <span begin="30.584" end="30.902">down</span> <span begin="30.902" end="31.239">to</span> <span begin="31.239" end="31.376">the</span> <span begin="31.376" end="32.200">floor</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我缓缓坠向地面</span></p><p begin="33.020" end="35.250" itunes:key="L5" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="33.020" end="33.275">Life</span> <span begin="33.275" end="33.730">was</span> <span begin="33.730" end="34.915">escaping</span> <span begin="34.915" end="35.250">me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">眼睁睁看着生命从我眼前溜走</span></p><p begin="35.500" end="37.626" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="35.500" end="35.782">I</span> <span begin="35.782" end="36.250">couldn&apos;t</span> <span begin="36.250" end="36.716">find</span> <span begin="36.716" end="37.626">myself</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我迷失了自己 如堕烟海</span></p><p begin="37.895" end="40.080" itunes:key="L7" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="37.895" end="38.238">&apos;Til</span> <span begin="38.238" end="38.507">it</span> <span begin="38.507" end="38.888">was</span> <span begin="38.888" end="39.354">all</span> <span begin="39.740" end="40.080">lost</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在我失去一切之前</span></p><p begin="40.080" end="41.550" itunes:key="L8" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="40.080" end="40.656">Not</span> <span begin="40.656" end="41.550">anymore</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我要勇敢地去把这一切拿回来</span></p><p begin="42.310" end="47.513" itunes:key="L9" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="42.310" end="42.488">I&apos;m</span> <span begin="42.488" end="42.916">holding</span> <span begin="42.916" end="43.066">on</span> <span begin="43.066" end="43.326">to</span> <span begin="43.326" end="43.501">all</span> <span begin="43.501" end="43.681">the</span> <span begin="43.681" end="44.292">pieces</span> <span begin="44.292" end="44.737">of</span> <span begin="44.737" end="44.902">my</span> <span begin="44.902" end="45.338">heart&apos;s</span> <span begin="45.338" end="46.100">debris</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">咬紧牙关 握紧我那支离破碎的心</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="45.840" end="47.513"><span begin="45.840" end="45.955">(Of</span> <span begin="45.955" end="46.095">my</span> <span begin="46.095" end="46.625">heart&apos;s</span> <span begin="46.625" end="47.513">debris)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我那支离破碎的心</span></span></p><p begin="47.332" end="49.146" itunes:key="L10" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="47.332" end="47.851">&apos;Til</span> <span begin="47.851" end="48.191">it&apos;s</span> <span begin="48.191" end="49.146">time</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">直到最后一刻</span></p><p begin="50.326" end="56.835" itunes:key="L11" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="50.326" end="51.099">I&apos;ll,</span> <span begin="51.959" end="52.184">I&apos;ll</span> <span begin="52.184" end="52.439">pull</span> <span begin="52.439" end="52.580">it</span> <span begin="52.580" end="53.156">together</span> <span begin="53.156" end="53.449">and</span> <span begin="53.449" end="53.772">fix</span> <span begin="53.772" end="54.429">myself</span> <span begin="54.429" end="56.133">eventually</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我会将它一一拼凑 最后不药而愈</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="55.780" end="56.835"><span begin="55.780" end="56.835">(Eventually)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">终会不药而愈</span></span></p><p begin="56.835" end="58.830" itunes:key="L12" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="56.835" end="57.029">I</span> <span begin="57.029" end="57.569">know</span> <span begin="57.569" end="57.921">it&apos;s</span> <span begin="57.921" end="58.830">mine</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我知道这是属于我的</span></p><p begin="59.128" end="1:01.586" itunes:key="L13" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="59.128" end="59.246">I</span> <span begin="59.246" end="59.694">found</span> <span begin="59.694" end="1:00.011">gold</span> <span begin="1:00.011" end="1:00.292">in</span> <span begin="1:00.292" end="1:00.636">the</span> <span begin="1:00.636" end="1:01.586">wreckage</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我在残垣断壁间拾到闪亮的金子</span></p><p begin="1:01.846" end="1:03.979" itunes:key="L14" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:01.846" end="1:02.148">Put</span> <span begin="1:02.148" end="1:02.475">it</span> <span begin="1:02.475" end="1:02.766">on</span> <span begin="1:02.766" end="1:03.081">a</span> <span begin="1:03.081" end="1:03.979">necklace</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">将它做成一串项链</span></p><p begin="1:04.260" end="1:08.567" itunes:key="L15" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:04.260" end="1:04.902">Keepin&apos;</span> <span begin="1:04.902" end="1:05.180">it</span> <span begin="1:05.180" end="1:05.549">&apos;cause</span> <span begin="1:05.549" end="1:05.812">I-</span><span begin="1:06.079" end="1:06.400">I-</span><span begin="1:06.723" end="1:07.198">I,</span> <span begin="1:07.198" end="1:07.318">I</span> <span begin="1:07.318" end="1:07.469">know</span> <span begin="1:07.469" end="1:07.620">that</span> <span begin="1:07.620" end="1:07.885">it&apos;s</span> <span begin="1:07.885" end="1:08.567">mine</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">好好地保管它 因为我知道这是属于我的</span></p><p begin="1:08.854" end="1:11.240" itunes:key="L16" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:08.854" end="1:09.092">I</span> <span begin="1:09.092" end="1:09.419">wear</span> <span begin="1:09.419" end="1:09.581">it</span> <span begin="1:09.581" end="1:09.902">like</span> <span begin="1:09.902" end="1:10.336">a</span> <span begin="1:10.336" end="1:11.240">message</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">这是我存在的痕迹</span></p><p begin="1:11.495" end="1:13.596" itunes:key="L17" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:11.495" end="1:11.903">So</span> <span begin="1:11.903" end="1:12.140">I</span> <span begin="1:12.140" end="1:12.309">don&apos;t</span> <span begin="1:12.309" end="1:13.298">forget</span> <span begin="1:13.298" end="1:13.596">it</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">所以我永远不会忘记它</span></p><p begin="1:13.980" end="1:18.445" itunes:key="L18" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:13.980" end="1:14.587">Keepin&apos;</span> <span begin="1:14.587" end="1:14.887">it</span> <span begin="1:14.887" end="1:15.218">&apos;cause</span> <span begin="1:15.218" end="1:15.467">I-</span><span begin="1:15.761" end="1:16.083">I-</span><span begin="1:16.389" end="1:16.863">I,</span> <span begin="1:16.863" end="1:17.026">I</span> <span begin="1:17.026" end="1:17.172">know</span> <span begin="1:17.172" end="1:17.317">that</span> <span begin="1:17.317" end="1:17.587">it&apos;s</span> <span begin="1:17.587" end="1:18.445">mine</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">好好地保管它 因为我知道这是属于我的</span></p><p begin="1:19.305" end="1:23.079" itunes:key="L19" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:19.305" end="1:19.438">I</span> <span begin="1:19.438" end="1:19.606">know</span> <span begin="1:19.606" end="1:19.739">that</span> <span begin="1:19.739" end="1:20.001">it&apos;s</span> <span begin="1:20.001" end="1:20.637">mine,</span> <span begin="1:21.238" end="1:21.856">mine,</span> <span begin="1:22.461" end="1:23.079">mine</span></p><p begin="1:24.128" end="1:27.918" itunes:key="L20" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:24.128" end="1:24.281">I</span> <span begin="1:24.281" end="1:24.461">know</span> <span begin="1:24.461" end="1:24.608">that</span> <span begin="1:24.608" end="1:24.862">it&apos;s</span> <span begin="1:24.862" end="1:25.484">mine,</span> <span begin="1:26.097" end="1:26.710">mine,</span> <span begin="1:27.321" end="1:27.918">mine</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我知道这是属于我的，我的，我的</span></p><p begin="1:28.997" end="1:32.785" itunes:key="L21" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:28.997" end="1:29.154">I</span> <span begin="1:29.154" end="1:29.311">know</span> <span begin="1:29.311" end="1:29.456">that</span> <span begin="1:29.456" end="1:29.728">it&apos;s</span> <span begin="1:29.728" end="1:30.339">mine,</span> <span begin="1:30.936" end="1:31.554">mine,</span> <span begin="1:32.153" end="1:32.785">mine</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我知道这是属于我的，我的，我的</span></p><p begin="1:33.860" end="1:37.769" itunes:key="L22" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:33.860" end="1:34.000">I</span> <span begin="1:34.000" end="1:34.158">know</span> <span begin="1:34.158" end="1:34.288">that</span> <span begin="1:34.288" end="1:34.592">it&apos;s</span> <span begin="1:34.592" end="1:35.184">mine,</span> <span begin="1:35.801" end="1:36.394">mine,</span> <span begin="1:37.008" end="1:37.769">mine</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我知道这是属于我的，我的，我的</span></p><p begin="1:41.126" end="1:42.504" itunes:key="L23" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:41.126" end="1:41.283">I</span> <span begin="1:41.283" end="1:41.439">know</span> <span begin="1:41.439" end="1:41.569">that</span> <span begin="1:41.569" end="1:41.904">it&apos;s</span> <span begin="1:41.904" end="1:42.504">mine</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我知道这是属于我的</span></p><p begin="1:50.803" end="1:52.454" itunes:key="L24" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:50.803" end="1:50.976">I</span> <span begin="1:50.976" end="1:51.105">know</span> <span begin="1:51.105" end="1:51.242">that</span> <span begin="1:51.242" end="1:51.578">it&apos;s</span> <span begin="1:51.578" end="1:52.454">mine</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我知道这是属于我的</span></p><p begin="1:55.640" end="1:59.754" itunes:key="L25" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:55.640" end="1:55.830">I</span> <span begin="1:55.830" end="1:55.933">know</span> <span begin="1:55.933" end="1:56.100">that</span> <span begin="1:56.100" end="1:56.395">it&apos;s</span> <span begin="1:56.395" end="1:57.031">mine,</span> <span begin="1:57.611" end="1:58.259">mine,</span> <span begin="1:58.828" end="1:59.754">mine</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我知道这是属于我的，我的，我的</span></p><p begin="2:02.628" end="2:04.750" itunes:key="L26" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:02.628" end="2:03.235">Facing</span> <span begin="2:03.235" end="2:03.608">the</span> <span begin="2:03.608" end="2:04.750">change</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">面对朝云暮雨的日子</span></p><p begin="2:05.178" end="2:07.324" itunes:key="L27" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:05.178" end="2:05.453">But</span> <span begin="2:05.453" end="2:05.793">it&apos;s</span> <span begin="2:05.793" end="2:06.076">still</span> <span begin="2:06.076" end="2:06.630">tough</span> <span begin="2:06.630" end="2:06.860">to</span> <span begin="2:06.860" end="2:07.324">see</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">让人很难去看清事物的本质</span></p><p begin="2:07.610" end="2:10.730" itunes:key="L28" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:07.610" end="2:07.748">At</span> <span begin="2:07.748" end="2:08.230">first</span> <span begin="2:08.230" end="2:08.383">I</span> <span begin="2:08.383" end="2:08.850">fought</span> <span begin="2:08.850" end="2:09.140">it</span> <span begin="2:09.140" end="2:09.598">all</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">最初我盲目地抵抗一切</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="2:09.717" end="2:10.730"><span begin="2:09.717" end="2:10.077">(Fought</span> <span begin="2:10.077" end="2:10.327">it</span> <span begin="2:10.327" end="2:10.730">all)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">抵抗一切</span></span></p><p begin="2:10.307" end="2:12.434" itunes:key="L29" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:10.307" end="2:10.557">I</span> <span begin="2:10.557" end="2:10.734">was</span> <span begin="2:10.734" end="2:11.245">so</span> <span begin="2:11.546" end="2:12.434">mean</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">那时的我太刻薄了</span></p><p begin="2:12.434" end="2:13.987" itunes:key="L30" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:12.434" end="2:12.610">I&apos;m</span> <span begin="2:12.610" end="2:13.029">still</span> <span begin="2:13.029" end="2:13.987">unsure</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">直到现在我也不确定</span></p><p begin="2:14.837" end="2:17.070" itunes:key="L31" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:14.837" end="2:15.156">How</span> <span begin="2:15.156" end="2:15.488">it&apos;s</span> <span begin="2:15.488" end="2:16.401">supposed</span> <span begin="2:16.401" end="2:16.700">to</span> <span begin="2:16.700" end="2:17.070">be?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">事情本应该是什么样子？</span></p><p begin="2:17.308" end="2:22.010" itunes:key="L32" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:17.308" end="2:17.606">I&apos;m</span> <span begin="2:17.606" end="2:18.218">taking</span> <span begin="2:18.218" end="2:19.441">everyday</span> <span begin="2:19.441" end="2:19.995">now</span> <span begin="2:19.995" end="2:20.364">by</span> <span begin="2:20.364" end="2:20.629">the</span> <span begin="2:20.629" end="2:20.981">skin</span> <span begin="2:20.981" end="2:21.241">of</span> <span begin="2:21.241" end="2:21.506">my</span> <span begin="2:21.506" end="2:22.010">teeth</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">现在的我每一件事都会切身去寻找 去体会</span></p><p begin="2:22.172" end="2:23.570" itunes:key="L33" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:22.172" end="2:22.719">Until</span> <span begin="2:22.719" end="2:23.094">I</span> <span begin="2:23.094" end="2:23.570">learn</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">直到我领悟</span></p><p begin="2:24.144" end="2:29.151" itunes:key="L34" ttm:agent="v1"><span